This page will be for prospective apprentices and will show all current apprenticeship opportunities.

//Search

The search function will be a way to filter results in a way that fits you.
You will be able to filter by: Location, Business, University, Industry, Subject, Term Time, Pay, Hours.

//Details Stored
The individual records will store data about: Location, Business, University, Industry, Subject, Term Time, Pay, Hours, The application process, contact details etc.